quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,14,"un se lrho, Allah tumahray hathon se un ko saza dlwaye ga aur inhen zaleel o khawar kere ga aur un ke muqaabla mein tumhari madad kere ga aur bohat se mominoun ke dil thanday kere ga"
9,15,"aur un ke qaloob ki jalan mita day ga, aur jisay chahay ga tauba ki tofeq bhi day ga Allah sab kuch jan-nay wala aur Dana hai"
9,16,"kya tum logon ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke yuhin chore diye jao ge halaank abhi Allah ne yeh to dekha hi nahi ke tum mein se kon woh log hain jinhon ne ( is ki raah mein ) jaan fashani ki aur Allah aur rasool aur momnin ke siwa kisi ko jigaree dost nah banaya, jo kuch tum karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
9,17,mushriqeen ka yeh kaam nahi hai ke woh Allah ki masjidoon ke Mujawer o khadim banindar-aa-n hala-n kehہ apne oopar woh khud kufar ki shahadat day rahay hain un ke to saaray aamaal zaya ho gay aur jahannum mein inhen hamesha rehna hai
9,18,"Allah ki masjidoon ke abad car ( Mujawer o khadim ) to wohi log ho saktay hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir ko manen aur numa zay qaim karen, zkoh den aur Allah ke siwa kisi se nah dareen unhi se yeh tawaqqa hai ke seedhi raah chalein ge"
9,19,kya tum logon ne hajion ko pani pilanay aur masjid haraam ki mjavri karne ko is shakhs ke kaam ke barabartehra liya hai jo imaan laya Allah par aur roz aakhir par aur jis ne jaanfishani ki Allah ki raah mein? Allah ke nazdeek to yeh dono barabar nahi hain aur Allah zaalmon ki rahnumai nahi karta
9,20,Allah ke haan to unhi logon ka darja bara hai jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne is ki raah mein ghar baar chhorey aur jaan o maal se jehaad kya wohi kamyaab hain
